<div id="pf4644" class="pf w5b h2f7" data-page-no="4644"><div class="pc pc4644 w5b h2f7"><div class="t m6c2 xb4 h5 y2457 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We know that in everything God </div><div class="t m385 xd6 h5 y2092 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works for good with those who love </div><div class="t mab xd6 h5 y20a7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him&quot; (Rom. 8:28, RSV). </div><div class="t m2ba xb4 h35 y27e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The book of Job does not provide a </div><div class="t m2a7 xd6 h35 y57e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complete answer to the problem of </div><div class="t m6c2 xd6 h35 y23e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pain. Job&apos;s experience shows why and </div><div class="t m1344 xd6 h35 y3fb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how one man suffered, and how God </div><div class="t m787 xd6 h35 y1479 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eventually revealed Himself to the </div><div class="t m697 xd6 h35 y88 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sufferer and reversed his fortunes. It </div><div class="t m5ef xd6 h35 y9aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cannot be concluded that every </div><div class="t m330 xd6 h35 yad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">person who suffers is an actor in a </div><div class="t m9b7 xd6 h35 yd6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">divine drama as was Job. </div><div class="t mda5 xb4 h35 yab4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Most of </div><div class="t m2b5 x61 h35 y9e2 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our </div><div class="t m9d2 x5b h35 y2da ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">headaches and </div><div class="t m95 xd6 h35 y198 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heartaches result from the normal </div><div class="t m141 xd6 h35 y29d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hazards of life in this world. We bring </div><div class="t m89e xd6 h35 y1d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disease on ourselves by not paying </div><div class="t m177 xd6 h35 y15fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attention to the laws of life and health. </div><div class="t mb9b xd6 h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We are all potential victims of </div><div class="t m72b xd6 h35 y585 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accident, viruses, disappointments, </div><div class="t m196 xd6 h35 y3f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">losses, and many other </div><div class="t m5dc x72 h5 y2f49 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 10 August 31 to September 6 </div><div class="t m368d x1c h1ed y2bbf ff2 fs40 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Berra</div><div class="t m18c0 xa7 h1ed y2b59 ff2 fs40 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m489b x57 h1ed y2b59 ff2 fs40 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n </div><div class="t m3b7 x1f h35 y28ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pain-producing factors. </div><div class="t m17f x1c h35 y237a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From Job we can learn of God&apos;s love </div><div class="t m4da x1f h35 y208d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for and patience with the sufferer. We </div><div class="t m819 x1f h35 y48 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can learn how &quot;God works for good </div><div class="t m50e x1f h35 y465 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with those who love him.&quot; But in many </div><div class="t m80c x1f h35 y2067 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">respects Job&apos;s experience was not </div><div class="t m146 x1f h35 y555 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">typical of everyday human life. The </div><div class="t m3af x1f h35 y8df ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">purpose of this lesson is to stress the </div><div class="t m16e x1f h35 y5de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth that the same God who helped </div><div class="t m161b x1f h35 y5b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job resolve his problems will help us </div><div class="t m1adf x1f h35 y14c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;in everything.&quot; God is concerned </div><div class="t m2c5 x1f h35 yac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about all kinds of pain, physical and </div><div class="t m74b x1f h35 y435 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mental. He looks with compassion on </div><div class="t m80 x1f h35 yd7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the father, worried about how to pay </div><div class="t m1745 x1f h35 y75b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the bills, and the mother, concerned </div><div class="t m976 x1f h35 y4c2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">about the bringing up of her children. </div><div class="t m9d8 x1f h35 yac4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He feels the pain of the cancer patient </div><div class="t m284 x1f h35 y48a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the heartache of the bereaved. He </div><div class="t mf22 x1f h35 ya26 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">does not promise to exempt us from </div><div class="t ma4c x1f h35 y8b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all these hazards as long as we are in </div><div class="t m452 x1f h35 y154 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the world. We must accept our lot as </div><div class="t m12d x1f h35 y1229 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fellow sufferers with all mankind. But </div><div class="t m96c x1f h35 ya5f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we must never forget that &quot;in </div><div class="t m490 x1f h35 yab5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everything God works for good with </div><div class="t m1516 x1f h35 y5b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those who love him.&quot; </div><div class="t m12eb x1c h35 y130 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whatever may be your </div><div class="t m603 x1f h35 ya61 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">circumstances, however dark and </div><div class="t m618 x1f h35 y26a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mysterious may be the ways of </div><div class="t m95 x1f h35 y55e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Providence, though the path may be </div><div class="t m3bb x1f h35 y41f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the deep waters, and trials </div><div class="t m5a6 x1f h35 y91c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and bereavements may afflict again </div><div class="t m5cf x1f h35 y96 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and again, the assurance still comes, </div><div class="t m119d x1f h35 y1c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;All things work together for good to </div><div class="t m16e x1f h35 y291 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them that love God.&apos; (Rom. 8:28).&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m44 x2b h35 yac8 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selected Messages, </div><div class="t m110 x94 h35 y356 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bk. 2, p. 261. </div><div class="t m558 x1f h5 y28 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m8af x1f h5 y75 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. God Feels Our Pain </div><div class="t m66f xb0 h5 yba4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 63:9) </div><div class="t m5b5 x1f h5 y77 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. God&apos;s Presence </div><div class="t m375 x6e h5 y1474 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 43:2, 3) </div><div class="t m2e6 x1f h5 y223 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. God Helps and Delivers </div><div class="t mf02 x6e h5 y5f3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Ps. 33:18-22) </div><div class="t m152 x1f h5 y278 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. Helping One Another </div><div class="t m8ac x6e h5 y1ae ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 12:26) </div><div class="t m9f x1f h5 y628 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. Pain With Courage </div><div class="t m15e x6e h5 yaea ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 4:8, 9; 1 Cor. 4:11-13) </div><div class="t m58a x1f h5 y395 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. Pain Will End </div><div class="t m759 x6e h5 yaa6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 21:4) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
